- DO YOU LIKE IT? I'VE SPENT
YEARS ON ITS CONSTRUCTION.

46
00:04:54,583 --> 00:04:56,875
AND NOW THAT I'VE FOUND YOU AND
YOUR OUTSTANDING ABILITIES,

47
00:04:56,958 --> 00:04:58,708
