00:11:29,833 --> 00:11:31,166
- ASHLEY.
- Woman on tv: DIRECTOR

180
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:32,666
COMMENDED THE EFFORTS OF THE

181
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,708
SECURITY TEAM IN BRINGING
DOWN THE SUSPECT CELICA YAYOI,

182
00:11:34,791 --> 00:11:36,875
AND ASSURED THE PUBLIC THAT
THE REMAINING SUSPECTS

183
00:11:36,958 --> 00:11:39,583
WOULD ALSO BE
BROUGHT TO JUSTICE.

184
00:11:41,708 --> 00:11:43,791
- I'VE SAT BY LONG ENOUGH.

185
00:11:43,875 --> 00:11:46,583
I CAN'T REMAIN A
SPECTATOR ANY LONGER.

186
00:11:54,416 --> 00:11:59,541
- I LOVE THIS CITY.
AND YET I DESPISE IT.

187
00:11:59,625 --> 00:12:03,416
AND I'LL CRUSH ANYONE
THAT STANDS IN MY WAY.

188
00:12:12,041 --> 00:12:15,416
- ( phone ringing )

189
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:19,250
- Mrs. Yayoi: WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU PEOPLE?

190
00:12:19,333 --> 00:12:21,916
YOU HOUND ME DAY AND NIGHT FOR
INTERVIEWS! CELICA WOULD NEVER

191
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,875
--DO ANYTHING LIKE THAT!
- I'M SORRY, MRS. YAYOI.

192
00:12:24,958 --> 00:12:28,625
- INTEGRA,
IS THAT YOU? IT IS YOU!

193
00:12:28,708 --> 00:12:31,708
PLEASE! TELL ME WHAT
HAPPENED TO MY LITTLE GIRL!

194
00:12:31,791 --> 00:12:34,125
YOU MUST KNOW
SOMETHING ABOUT ALL THIS!

195
00:12:34,208 --> 00:12:36,750
YOU GIRLS WERE LIKE
SISTERS! PLEASE--

196
00:12:38,208 --> 00:12:41,125
- ( crying ) I'M SO SORRY.

197
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,791
- HEY.

198
00:12:47,083 --> 00:12:50,250
- AXELA THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANT TO SHOW YOU.

199
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:57,916
- HMM. IS THIS THING
RECORDING OR WHAT?

200
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:01,083
LOOKS LIKE IT IS. YEAH,
THE LITTLE RED LIGHT IS ON.

201
00:13:01,708 --> 00:13:03,208
( clears throat )

202
00:13:03,291 --> 00:13:06,625
OKAY. I DECIDED THAT IF I TRIED
TO WRITE THIS DOWN IN A LETTER,

203
00:13:06,708 --> 00:13:08,166
I WOULD NEVER HAVE
BEEN ABLE TO FINISH,

204
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:10,208
THAT, PLUS I TOTALLY
SUCK AT WRITING,

205
00:13:10,291 --> 00:13:13,625
SO HERE WE GO. OH, MY GOD,
THIS IS A LOT MORE EMBARRASSING

206
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:14,833
THAN I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE.

207
00:13:14,916 --> 00:13:18,041
JUST BEAR WITH ME,
THIS WILL BE OVER SOON.

208
00:13:18,125 --> 00:13:21,791
LET'S SEE, INTEGRA?

209
00:13:21,875 --> 00:13:25,208
I'M REALLY SORRY FOR ALL THE
TROUBLE THAT I'VE CAUSED YOU.

210
00:13:25,291 --> 00:13:28,791
IT'S JUST, TOO BAD THAT
THINGS ENDED UP THIS WAY.

211
00:13:28,875 --> 00:13:30,041
( laughs ) LISTEN TO ME!

212
00:13:30,125 --> 00:13:33,083
SOUNDS LIKE THESE ARE MY
LAST WORDS OR SOMETHING.

213
00:13:33,166 --> 00:13:34,666
- WHATEVER. ANYWAY.
- CELICA...

214
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:38,000
OH! AXELA! I NEED YOU
TO DO ME A FAVOR.

215
00:13:38,083 --> 00:13:39,541
IF ANYTHING YOU KNOW...

216
00:13:39,625 --> 00:13:41,416
IF ANYTHING SHOULD HAPPEN TO ME,

217
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,583
